Interface CameraVidSourceOrder

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<CameraVidSourceOrder>, SonarObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
CameraVidSourceOrderImpl
public interface CameraVidSourceOrder extends SonarObject, Comparable<CameraVidSourceOrder>
CameraVidSourceOrder: an interface for objects that bind a camera-template to a source- template and provide a sort order. The pair of camera-template and order-number will be unique.
Author:
John L. Stanley - SRF Consulting
